    "Name": "Arbalest",
    "Details": "This variation of the standard Arbalest, developed in 3081, focuses on improving the capabilities of the 'Mech by using ferro-fibrous armor to increase protection. The Arbalest 3 also replaces the ECM suite with an extra ton of armor to increase protection further. The two arm-mounted lasers are swapped out for a pair of ER small lasers.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Ubiquitous</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.02</color></b>",
